---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <main class="flex-1 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 w-full">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Me</h1>
    
    <article class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p>
        Hi! I'm Akhil Panchal, a Software Engineer passionate about building great web experiences.
        I love working with modern frontend technologies and exploring the intersection of design and code.
      </p>

      <p>
        When I'm not coding, you can find me singing, cycling, or exploring new music.
        I'm particularly fond of indie music and love discovering talented independent artists.
      </p>

      <h2>What I Do</h2>
      <p>
        I specialize in frontend development, with expertise in React, TypeScript, and modern web technologies.
        I'm passionate about creating performant, accessible, and beautiful user interfaces.
      </p>

      <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Feel free to connect with me on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/akhilpanchal" target="_blank"
          rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a> or
        check out my projects on <a href="https://github.com/akhilpanchal" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>